These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: soy-milk, juice, iced-tea, almond-milk
Pet: turtle, lizard, hamster, chinchilla
1. Pet:chinchilla is on the left of Beverage:iced-tea##1
2. Beverage:soy-milk is on the left of Pet:lizard##1
3. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:hamster is on the left or right of Pet:chinchilla##3
5. Beverage:soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Pet        | turtle | lizard   | chinchilla | hamster    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: adventure, thriller, spy, action
Nationality: spanish, malaysian, indian, japanese
1. Movie-Genre:thriller is on the left of Movie-Genre:action##1
2. Nationality:spanish is on the left of Nationality:indian##1
3. Nationality:indian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:spanish == Movie-Genre:adventure##1
5. Nationality:malaysian is on the right of Nationality:indian##1
6. Nationality:spanish == Movie-Genre:adventure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | adventure  | thriller  | action |
| Nationality   | japanese    | spanish | indian | malaysian    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: lettuce, orange, kiwi, asparagus
Movie-Genre: sports, adventure, superhero, family
1. Food:asparagus is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:family##3
2. Food:kiwi is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:family is on the left or right of Food:orange##3
4. Movie-Genre:family is on the right of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
5. Movie-Genre:sports is in an odd position##4
6. Food:orange is on the right of Food:kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | asparagus | kiwi | orange    | lettuce      |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero        | family     | sports | adventure |

