.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: board-games, sudoku, gardening, writing
Music-Genre: hip-hop, trance, house, d&b
1. Hobby:sudoku is between Music-Genre:hip-hop and Music-Genre:d&b##2
2. Hobby:writing is on the left of Hobby:board-games##1
3. Music-Genre:house is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:trance is on the left of Music-Genre:d&b##1
5. Music-Genre:trance is on the right of Hobby:board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | writing | board-games | sudoku | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | house       | hip-hop   | trance    | d&b  |

