.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: salsa, country, trance, indie
Nationality: thai, polish, egyptian, dutch
1. Music-Genre:trance is on the right of Nationality:dutch##1
2. Nationality:polish == Music-Genre:indie##1
3. Nationality:egyptian is on the right of Music-Genre:salsa##1
4. Music-Genre:country is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:trance is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:thai is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | country  | salsa    | trance   | indie       |
| Nationality   | thai | dutch | egyptian | polish |

