4. Job:dancer is on the right of Pet:cat##1
5. Job:photographer is between Job:dancer and Job:manager##2
6. Pet:hamster is in an odd position##4
7. Pet:hamster is between Job:photographer and Pet:hedgehog##2
8. Job:photographer is on the left or right of Job:manager##3

