.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: iced-tea, 7up, coffee, water
Music-Genre: indie, d&b, folk, gospel
1. Beverage:iced-tea == Music-Genre:gospel##1
2. Music-Genre:indie is on the right of Beverage:iced-tea##1
3. Music-Genre:gospel is between Music-Genre:indie and Beverage:coffee##2
4. Beverage:iced-tea is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:gospel is on the left or right of Music-Genre:indie##3
6. Beverage:7up is on the left or right of Music-Genre:d&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up       | coffee   | iced-tea | water |
| Music-Genre   | folk | d&b | gospel        | indie    |

