.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: iced-tea, coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
Food: papaya, lettuce, grapefruit, cabbage
1. Food:lettuce is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Beverage:iced-tea##3
3. Beverage:soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:grapefruit is on the left of Food:cabbage##1
5. Food:cabbage is on the right of Beverage:iced-tea##1
6. Food:grapefruit is in an even position##4
7. Food:papaya == Beverage:coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | iced-tea    | hot-chocolate       | coffee |
| Food       | lettuce  | grapefruit | cabbage | papaya  |

