.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
Job: teacher, fisherman, freelancer, engineer
Transport: bike, quad-bike, bus, motorbike
1. Job:fisherman is in an even position##4
2. Job:fisherman is on the left or right of Transport:bike##3
3. Transport:quad-bike is between Job:teacher and Transport:bike##2
4. Job:fisherman is on the far left or far right##3
5. Transport:bus is on the right of Job:engineer##1
6. Transport:bus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | teacher | freelancer   | engineer | fisherman |
| Transport   | motorbike          | quad-bike | bike         | bus  |

 